lifeaquatic.manuals.almanac.chapters.tools.wrench.title=Pearlescent Wrench
lifeaquatic.manuals.almanac.chapters.tools.wrench.page0=The general go-to tool for any aspiring undersea explorer is the §1Pearlescent Wrench§8.<br><br>It is made from a pearl, some tin, and two iron ingots.<br><br>Right-clicking on a device will rotate it, while doing so while sneaking will instantly dismantle it.

# --- --- Lens
lifeaquatic.manuals.almanac.chapters.tools.lens.title=Inquisitor's Lens
lifeaquatic.manuals.almanac.chapters.tools.lens.page0=For when things go wrong, reach for the §5Inquisitor's Lens§8 to help give you a closer look at your machines.<br><br>Right-clicking on a device with the lens will show debugging information about that device, and report any problems it might have.

